name: The Beast FPO - Nokia Disc Golf Park
notes:

liveLayoutDetails.notes:
Triple Mandatory (804.01): Discs may not enter the restricted space marked by orange line and the outside edges of the gate. 

For throws that miss the mandatory the next throw is limited to the previous lie with a one stroke penalty.
